name: witch
description: The second work of three, which more precisely conveys the atmosphere of the film Gaspar Noe «Lux Æterna». There’s a beautiful girl here who matches up with a beautiful witch from the movie. The new color of the picture is purple, another bright color that stands out. This is often used by the director.  Neon colors change each other last 10 minutes in the film «Lux Æterna», and they dissolve human figures. Epileptic light brings bliss beyond all the joys of life: nothing supernatural can ever be comfortable.
